Package: tntf
Title: Tuesday Night Football Analytics Platform
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("TNF", "Analytics", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "faisalmushtaq@gmail.com")
Description: Ingests messy Tuesday Night Football team sheets, standardises
    player names through an alias lookup, stores results in a tidy relational
    model and serves match, player, partnership, head-to-head, network and
    time-series analytics through a Shiny dashboard and an optional PDF
    report.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.3)
Imports:
    dplyr, tidyr, tibble, purrr, readr, stringr, forcats, ggplot2,
    lubridate, scales, igraph, tidygraph, ggraph, ggrepel, ggridges,
    ggalluvial, viridis, shiny, bslib, DT, plotly, rmarkdown, knitr,
    kableExtra
Suggests:
    testthat, ggprism, gt, reactable, janitor, patchwork
